&lt;p style="line-height: 15.8079996109009px;"&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: 15.8079996109009px;"&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: 15.8079996109009px;"&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: 15.8079996109009px;"&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &amp;lt;div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12"&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: 15.8079996109009px;"&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &amp;lt;i class="fa fa-quote-left" style="color: #ddd; font-size: 150%;"&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt; &amp;lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&amp;gt;The CCEx helps institutions in two respects: On the one hand it supports comparing different approaches and implementations of digital preservation, helps evaluating performances and provides quality assurance. On the other hand it emphasises to our funding bodies the cost-efficient, systematical and collaborative way the cultural domain deals with digital preservation; this creates trust in our activities.&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt; &amp;lt;i class="fa fa-quote-right" style="color: #ddd; font-size: 150%; position: absolute; margin: 5px 0 0 3px;"&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
