&lt;p style="line-height: 15.8079996109009px;"&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &amp;lt;i class="fa fa-quote-left" style="color: #ddd; font-size: 150%;"&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt; &amp;lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&amp;gt;The CCEx is an innovative idea that helps to solve the problem faced by universities and research data managers of how to estimate and allocate the resources required to fulfil their business and research excellence obligations.&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt; &amp;lt;i class="fa fa-quote-right" style="color: #ddd; font-size: 150%; position: absolute; margin: 5px 0 0 3px;"&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
